<?Include resource=500?>
<PageInfo title="Move a view window to another monitor"/>

<xPageTitle>
	Move a view window to another monitor
</xPageTitle>

<p>
	<xLN/> supports multiple monitors if you have them installed
	and working. (To find out more search in Windows Help for "Multiple monitors" or
	talk to your local computer guru.)
</p>

<p>
	To move a view window to the next monitor:
</p>

<ol>
	<li>
		Press the <xButtonNextMonitor/> button.
	</li>
</ol>
